Package HdbOfficer

Class HdbOfficerController

java.lang.Object
HdbOfficer.HdbOfficerController
All Implemented Interfaces:
UserController
public class HdbOfficerController extends Object implements UserController
Controller for managing HDB Officer functionalities. Handles the interaction between HDB Officer UI and other components such as project, application, enquiry, and report management.
